cu.explanation_en: Setting the ciphering algorithm to the unknown enum 'nea9' will cause negotiation failure during the security negotiation phase and NAS registration rejection.

du.explanation_en: Setting prach_msg1_FDM to 10 (valid values are 0-3) will cause invalid configuration error during PRACH setup and cell initialization failure.
du.explanation_zh: 將 prach_msg1_FDM 設定為 10（有效值為 0-3）會在 PRACH 設定期間導致無效配置錯誤，並造成小區初始化失敗。
